<p>Neglecting specialized storage is perhaps the most costly mistake programs make with football lockers. Without proper helmet and shoulder pad storage, equipment becomes damaged, locker rooms become cluttered, and professional appearances suffer. Programs that prioritize specialized storage protect their equipment investment and create better environments.</p>

